#Snap Rodent and Pest Control Website

A single page website built for Snap Rodent and Pest Control. The goal is simple navigation, strong visuals, and minimal pages. The site highlights services, pricing, social media, and contact options. Each section is structured for fast scanning because users have short attention spans.

#Features

• Hero section with logo and American flag visual
• Service categories arranged as visual cards
• Simple pricing box
• Contact form with three essential fields
• Social media section for TikTok, Instagram, and Facebook
• Embedded customer reviews and before or after photos
• Mobile responsive layout
• Smooth scroll navigation

#Project Purpose

This project provides a modern website for the business owner and serves as hands-on practice with layout design, responsive structure, and real client workflow.

